11.3 Unit Economics

Hardware (CMV Kit):

· Bill of Materials: $38
· Assembly/test: $7
· Shipping/distribution: $3
· Total Cost: $48
· Sale Price: $50 (at cost)
· Lifetime Value: $84 (3 years of $1/month subscription)

Service Economics:

· Cloud infrastructure cost/user: $0.15/month
· Support cost/user: $0.10/month
· Transaction processing: $0.005/transaction
· Gross Margin: 75% on services

Break-even: 8 months at $1/month subscription

